CHANGES
=======

3.2.0
-----

* Add explicit install of net-snmp
* Change upstream URL for puppet-contrail
* Midonet element now complies with version 5.2
* Install ceph-selinux in overcloud-{controller,cephstorage} images

3.1.0
-----

* Installing openstack-sahara-ui
* Updating .gitreview for stable/mitaka
* Add python-cradox package to controllers
* Gnocchi Integration

2.0.0
-----

* Add overcloud-base element
* Deprecated tox -downloadcache option removed
* Change upstream URL of puppet-pacemaker
* Install puppet-zaqar
* Add puppet-kmod into image
* Trove Integration
* Add logging components
* Add monitoring dependencies
* Update deric-zookeeper reference in midonet image
* Use a stable version of MidoNet Neutron Plugin
* overcloud-controller: install python-networking-odl
* py26 is no longer supported by Infra's CI
* Remove Cassandra repository for MidoNet element
* Add Aodh component
* controller: install python-redis
* Install puppet-timezone via puppet-modules element
* Install puppet-mistral via puppet-modules element

